{"title":"PEAT description panel","type":"markdown","aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"# PEAT Overview
This dashboard shows information from the PEAT OT device collection tool including:
- List of devices found by PEAT
- Simple statistics of interest - unique log events, changing firmware/logic hashes
- Full list of events from logs from OT devices

If you don't see data in this dashboard, you'll need to ingest data with the PEAT tool and tell PEAT to dump the data into the Malcolm database like `./peat parse ./peat-results -e http://username:password@malcolm:9200` where `peat-results` is the output from a PEAT scan, pull or other data collection."}}
